      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 employed under institutional SQA protocol. Version control, build verification, and regression test suite documented. Solver passes all relevant FDA-nominated benchmark cases. Gradation 2 achieved and required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
